# Maintainer-only project tracking. SweetClaude state, Claude Code harness
# settings, and Claude Code project instructions stay local — not shipped in
# the published repo. (Scrubbed from history via git filter-repo; gitignored
# here so a stray `git add .` can't reintroduce them.)
.sweetclaude/
.claude/
strategy/
CLAUDE.md
